data.description: Completely renovated in 2022.This 3 bedroom 2 bath single-family home is absolutely LOVELY! Located on 1.17 partially cleared acres, sensational privacy. The roof was replaced in February 2021, remodeled kitchen with shaker cabinets and quartz countertops includes all kitchen appliances, washer, and dryer. Beautifully 3x3 feet porcelain tile throughout. 2022 updated modern design bathrooms, vaulted ceilings with new light fixtures.  Fantastic location in Golden Gate Estates. Don't miss out on this Great Opportunity to be the new owner.
